     <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage"><strong>Money Matters - Why should you pay us?</strong></span></div>
        <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">Every individual is different: their needs, desires and dreams. But it is the need to have a secure future that binds them all. And with the highly talented team of Financial Planners we know exactly how to enrich and secure the financial lives of our clients.</span></div>
        <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">For each and every planner in our team, your priorities come first. We are allied with you, not any financial institution. We charge fees to help provide you with unbiased advice, counseling, planning and implementation.</span></div>
    
    <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage"><strong>How much Fees do you need to pay us?</strong></span></div>
        <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
           Fees are based on the plan you choose. You will know up front exactly what you will receive as a part of the plan that you opt for. Our clients are not obligated to proceed with financial planning unless they are completely comfortable about their plan and their planner.
           We are confident that you will find value in the plan our financial planner creates for you. With your active involvement and inputs, you can enhance the value of your financial plan.  
        </span></div>
        <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
           We, at Ffreedom, know and understand the value of your money. And if you feel that we have not delivered what we promise you, or if you feel unhappy about the way the plan is proceeding, you can discontinue our services.  
        </span></div>
        
