    <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage"><strong>The First Meeting is Complimentary :</strong></span></div>
        <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
           The initial meeting with our advisors is Complimentary &amp; will help you answer all your doubts that you have about financial planning. Rest assured you do not have to pay us till you are satisfied about the need for financial planning.
        </span></div>
        <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
           Our planners will answer your queries about costs and fees and will present you with a complete picture of the course of action that they would take with your interest in mind.
        </span></div>   

   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage"><strong>Financial planning is a journey, not a destination :</strong></span> </div>
   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
      Our advisors frequently get asked by clients about how soon reviews of financial plans need to happen? Every phase in life presents itself with a challenge that, at times cannot be tackled alone, including financial woes.
    </span></div> 
   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
      While financial plans are created with an assessment of your short-term and long-term goals, over a period of time our priorities change and so do market conditions. To tackle such eventualities, our plans include period review of your progress.
    </span></div> 
   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
      For best results, we advise our clients to collaborate with our advisors on a semiannual to yearly basis to help you derive optimum returns from your assets and investments. This time frame may certainly change depending upon the situation and need of the client. Problems and woes may change its time and course, but reliable advisors are the assets that stay true. Please be advised that a renewal fee is charged at the time of reviewal.
    </span></div>
   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
      Financial Planning is not a onetime process and to fulfill your dreams and aspirations we will always be available to assist you. 
    </span></div>
